---
description: Repository / data access layer
globs: services/*/src/db/**/*.ts, services/*/src/repos/**/*.ts
alwaysApply: false
---
# Repos / Data Access

- One repo per aggregate or domain.
- Functions named for intent: `findById`, `createMessage`, `listConversations`.
- Return domain types — never raw DB rows.
- Use Drizzle ORM. Raw SQL needs a comment justification.
- Transactions are explicit — passed in when spanning multiple operations.
